{"tid":1658891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要勇武，但唔係白白消耗於街頭，而係燒真正嘅春袋","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:23:34.000Z","uid":237194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe0fc94b86c8675fca5f5792fdf4e251e9fb47c","tid":1658891,"uid":237194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"首先，好感激勇武寶寶4個月來嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係你地爭取到逃犯條例修訂嘅正式撤回同埋讓示威力量星火燎原！<br />\n<br />\n但係，街頭武力抗爭，導致每個星期大量手足被捕、受傷，甚至面對殺人滅口威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我地係時候諗下，係咪仲係一成不變咁走落去呢？<br />\n<br />\n街頭武力已經被黑警捉到哂路<br />\n我地同全副武裝嘅黑警一定係冇得打<br />\n就算比你打到幾隻落單狗，比你整爛哂Ｄ紅綠燈，政府第二日一樣正常運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭真正嘅力量，係在於要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">干擾社會運作</span></strong></span><br />\n所以勇武應該衝嘅時間唔係星期六日／夜晚<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>平日、日頭、返工時間</strong></span><br />\n應該衝嘅地點唔係街頭<br />\n而係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真正嘅春袋，例如稅局、政府合署</strong></span></span>，以至玩大Ｄ就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>中環區嘅銀行、港交所</strong></span></span>等等<br />\n<br />\n點樣做到？<br />\n我地下一步應該用大約兩星期時間去籌備下一次<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大三罷</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且罷左工唔係喺屋企9 hea等集會，而係要用盡一切辦法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">干擾社會運作</span></strong></span><br />\n當天朝早開始，分區集結於各區<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>政府合署</strong></span>，或者可以集中五區/七區政府合署<br />\n唔需要用好高武力，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>入去政府合署佔領、裝飾、整連儂牆、噴下漆</strong></span>已經好夠<br />\n重點係人要夠多，多人就做咩都得<br />\n目的<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>係逼公務員提早收工，影響政府運作</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足夠多嘅，可以擴大戰線去埋各區<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>中資銀行</strong></span>，用口號大大聲提醒市民，D錢放喺中資銀行好唔安全架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手法一樣係佔領、裝飾等等<br />\n目的係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">逼銀行落閘收皮</span></strong></span><br />\n外資銀行可以再諗下放唔放佢地一馬囉<br />\n<br />\n當日和理非出嚟負責包圍、掩護、叫口號、文宣<br />\n勇武就梗係幫手開門比各位寶寶進入政府大樓同各銀行瘋狂參觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府合署、銀行面積唔大，每區有1000個手足已經夠做有突啦<br />\n<br />\n除左機場之外，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>政府部門</strong></span>同埋<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>金融機構</strong></span>就係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>政府最大嘅春袋</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸爆香港隻金蛋，邊個泵水比港共政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其死喺街頭，不如用死前最後一口氣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">揸爆佢春袋</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba21548dd05ba31467d0f9f33f43d61adc13a5fa","tid":1658891,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"882b6324089dd3ffd4e7ae757edba4426ab61d6e","tid":1658891,"uid":237194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:11:10.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"3492b7dce1855008875ea47a7bde4ec5274aedfc","tid":1658891,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"係有諗頭 但有啲理想化 <br />\n而家啲狗行動一開波就衝出黎 所以和理非未成功可能就比狗嚇走<br />\n結果又係濫捕 同捉走寶貴嘅手足們<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d141639f3310908d44927b7866d47d8655a3842","tid":1658891,"uid":237194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3492b7dce1855008875ea47a7bde4ec5274aedfc","tid":1658891,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"係有諗頭 但有啲理想化 <br />\n而家啲狗行動一開波就衝出黎 所以和理非未成功可能就比狗嚇走<br />\n結果又係濫捕 同捉走寶貴嘅手足們<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"無論星期六日大遊行、分區集會，都一樣被狗捉、嚇<br />\n與其死喺街頭，不如死喺佢春袋<br />\n如果D狗喺政府大樓、銀行隔尼發癲，效果一樣係逼人落閘收工<br />\n佢要封交通就仲好，全港被罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n區區都有政府合署，大家行路去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}